            <p:rationale>It is most efficient to manage Business logic as much as possible from a single place. Defining, embedding, and hard-coding business rules into the integration infrastructure will make it much more difficult to migrate data and integrate applications. In the future, Business logic can be "full of State", which is contrary to the principle of stateless data. </p:rationale>
